article_title: Key Free Clinic offers patients dignified care
article_text:
The Key Free Clinic has been offering non-emergency medical care to Key Peninsula residents since 2013

Run by a volunteer medical staff, the clinic offers a range of medical care for all ages

The clinic has expanded to meet patient needs and is now open every Thursday from 5:30 to 8 p.m.

article_metadata.description: While going to the doctor is never fun, it is a relief to receive medical care when an injury or illness interrupts daily life.
